{"tid":1025649,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"印度政府認為抖音散播低劣文化 考慮禁止使用","createTime":"2019-02-17T13:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T08:34:45.000Z","uid":123991,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22667bfe07167486abff72612d7e7fa6938a5bb5","tid":1025649,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:14:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/tiktok.0.png.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Ftiktok.0.png.jpeg&h=98ee4aab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在中國非常流行的短片分享平台抖音，在外國也以 TikTok 的名義廣泛流傳，而且越來越普及。不過印度方面就認為抖音宣傳低俗文化，考慮禁止印度用家使用這軟件。<br />\n<br />\n之前在印度曾經有議員對於抖音（TikTok）表達擔憂，認為它成為引起激進爭論，亦不受法律和社會秩序的管制，並令色情內容流通。印度資訊科技部長 M. Manikandan 指，泰米爾納德邦政府建議禁止使用這個軟件。<br />\n<br />\n對於抖音令不當內容流通的指控並非首次，印度的議員一直擔心這個平台會令 Deepfakes 虛假影片更容易流傳，也容易成為網上欺凌的工具。這並不只是空穴來風，據當地傳媒報道，去年 12 月就已經有 36 個青少年因為在抖音被網絡欺凌而致電防止自殺熱線，更已經有 1 人自殺。印度的抖音活躍用家目前約有 2 千萬，抖音方面則回應指，他們會繼續會與印度政府溝通，以改善對用家的保障。<br />\n<br />\n來源：Verge <a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/2/13/18223590/tiktok-india-ban-legislation-government-teens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2019%2F2%2F13%2F18223590%2Ftiktok-india-ban-legislation-government-teens&d=MHEGAcVJLkfiWkVsZ9yRxkzob1WjLKDnR9IVaUJYWuI%3D&h=9a28720c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theverge.com/2019/2/13/18223590/tiktok-india-ban-legislation-government-teens</a>"},{"pid":"adb769b4e90f0fe0b0b47b745da2ce7ec8752cce","tid":1025649,"uid":192491,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家ban另一垃圾國家既野"},{"pid":"0a5105866c53806e6ad7cc8d6e0c93f25c6db968","tid":1025649,"uid":95470,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾之間有相互排斥性"},{"pid":"dde8ed6bac42bddc5db08aa7001c8566d3de725a","tid":1025649,"uid":183302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:46:38.000Z"